                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-187-victim1687 t18320405-187-viclabel1126"></join> to Henry Harben, a <rs id="t18320405-187-viclabel1127" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-187-victim1685 t18320405-187-viclabel1127"></join>, of High-street, Bloomsbury. On Friday afternoon, the 30th of March, I left the prisoner in care of my cart, in <placeName id="t18320405-187-crimeloc1128">Watling-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320405-187-crimeloc1128" type="placeName" value="Watling-street"></interp>
