                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-187-off1124 t18320405-187-crimeloc1128"></join>, while I went into a public-house - I returned in five minutes, and he was gone; I missed from the flap of the cart a parcel, containing 5s. in copper, and gave information to the Policeman when I got home - he had gone with me from my master's door, as a friend.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-187-person1689">
                  MAURICE 
                  NICHOLAS
               <interp inst="t18320405-187-person1689" type="surname" value="NICHOLAS"></interp>
